---
import Currently from '@/components/Currently'
---

<section class="w-full my-0 mt-16 flex flex-col gap-2 space-y-8 font-sans">
  <div
    class="md:gap-auto ml-auto flex w-full flex-col justify-between gap-10 md:flex-row"
  >
    <div class="about-col flex w-full flex-col gap-4 text-justify">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-sans opacity-75">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-accent">(About me)</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
        <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col gap-4">
          <span>
            Hey, I'm{' '}
            <span class="font-serifItalic text-accent"> Sasank Reddy </span>
            , I'm studying Computer Science at Amrita School of Engineering. I like
            designing and coding, and sometimes I play CTFs.{' '}
          </span>
          <p>
            I'm a student who loves learning. I may not have a fancy mission,
            but my passion for gaining knowledge and mastering new skills keeps
            me going.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="about-col flex w-full flex-col gap-4 text-justify">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-sans opacity-75">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-accent">(Currently)</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-8">
        <Currently client:load />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between font-sans opacity-75">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-accent">(Methodology)</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-8">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h1 class="font-serifItalic text-accent">Research</h1>
        <p>
          I start by understanding the problem, the audience, and the market.
          This involves analyzing similar products, defining goals, and
          gathering all necessary context.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h1 class="font-serifItalic text-accent">Design</h1>
        <p>
            Based on the research, I create user flows, wireframes, and high-fidelity designs. I focus on usability, visual identity, and a consistent experience across the app.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h1 class="font-serifItalic text-accent">Developing</h1>
        <p>
            I turn designs into functional apps using clean, scalable code. I prioritize performance, responsiveness, and a seamless user interface backed by solid architecture.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h1 class="font-serifItalic text-accent">Handoff</h1>
        <p>
            Once development is complete, I prepare documentation and assets for deployment or client delivery. I ensure everything is maintainable and easy for others to continue working on.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
